		(uuid "3ff1e5f5-119b-40a2-91c9-864270b9bcd1")
	)
	(text "This ADC monitor VMON from DAC8734 and the power supply output state."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 336.55 44.196 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "6581829a-2780-4707-ad8d-6d7880874076")
	)
	(text "TLA2021 doesnt support programmable scalling, vmon needs to go from 3.6V to 2.048V"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 124.46 135.89 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "66d0ff78-1f4a-492e-aac0-e68917c4fc58")
	)
	(text "VOUT-X-MAX = 3.6V"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 56.134 107.696 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "99e58d77-4609-4ec6-825d-f42c2d0aa7df")
	)
	(text "The voltage divider network should be small sized resistors. The input impedance of the ADC is high in the range of mega ohms.\n\nThe FSR is +- 2.048V only for TLA2021. The VDSS is set to 5V. \n\nVMON max = max 3.6V \n\nADDR slave address set to: 1001 000"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 299.974 56.134 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "9cdcf3d1-bae6-4604-bda5-f27111de8d4a")
	)
	(text "The AIN FS is +-2.048V for TLA2021. The input VMON will be max 3.6V. \nThis needs scalling. The details are shown in the schematics. \nThe resistors values are chosen in the selected range to keep the current flow bellow continuous current limit of 0.5 mA."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 300.482 16.51 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "9e6dc4ff-38c1-450d-9903-2c272fd321a5")
	)
	(text "I2C \n\nStandard-Mode 100KHZ; max rise time = 1000ns; max fall time = 250ns\nFast-Mode 400KHZ; max rise time = 300ns; max fall time = 300ns\n\nPull up size 4.7 KHz for compromise between rise times and current consumption \nFast-Mode may require scaling down for stronger drive and lower rise times."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 299.974 94.488 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "c218584c-261d-4f41-8f73-bd164405c2e1")
	)
